### List actions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wizard/actions

### Invoke action
POST http://localhost:3000/api/wizard/actions/scaffold-component/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inputs": { "componentName": "Card", "package": "packages/halo-ui" }
}

### Await invocation (replace with real ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wizard/invocations/{{invocationId}}

### Fetch artifact (replace with real ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wizard/artifacts/{{artifactId}}
